7 Hours Ago The journalist, who is also a resident of the town, said the Emir has addressed his subjects at his palace. It is unclear if any ransom was paid but the bandits earlier demanded N200 million for the release of the 85-year-old monarch. Gunmen had on Sunday morning abducted Kajuru and 13 of his family members in his palace.